		"And then I need to make sure the weeds haven't destroyed her garden yet..."
		"and I haven't picked up the treehouse in days..."
		"will it even rain tomorrow...?"
		--
		"\f[italic,0]"
	}
	Select.dreamgrrteasel
	{
		posact += 1
		"I'm his best friend,\w4 but he's not mine.\w8 I have to pretend like he is though because then he'll get upset and people will start asking questions about \w2''oh why aren't you friends anymore'',\w4 and ''what happened to you and Teasel'',\w2 which isn't worth dealing with.\w8\n\nEven if we stopped being friends I've got to fake relationships with everyone else out here, so it won't actually alleviate that much stress.\n\n\w8\s[2]* (They sigh.)\n\n\w8It's fine, \w5I'll work through it.\n\n\w8Thank you for giving me time to talk."
	}

